<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <style>
    .container {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #f7f7f7;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #333;
    }
    .code {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      font-size: 24px;
      color: white;
      background-color: #28a745;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
  </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="header">Email Verification</h2>
            <p>Dear Customer,</p>
            <p>Thank you for registering with PRO2052 Restaurant. Please use the
                following verification code to complete your registration:</p>
            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;">
                <span class="code">{{verificationCode}}</span>
            </div>
            <p>If you did not request this, please ignore this email.</p>
            <p>Best regards,<br />PRO2052 Restaurant Team</p>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
